<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Muhammed Shifan | Football Portfolio</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#050505;
    color:white;
    overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* Animated Background */
.bg-animation{
    position:fixed;
    width:100%;
    height:100%;
    top:0;
    left:0;
    z-index:-1;
    overflow:hidden;
}

.bg-animation span{
    position:absolute;
    display:block;
    width:20px;
    height:20px;
    background:#00ff88;
    border-radius:50%;
    animation:float 12s linear infinite;
    opacity:0.2;
}

@keyframes float{
    0%{
        transform:translateY(100vh) scale(0);
    }
    100%{
        transform:translateY(-100vh) scale(2);
    }
}

/* Hero */
.hero{
    min-height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{
    font-size:4rem;
    color:#00ff88;
    text-shadow:0 0 25px #00ff88;
    animation:glow 2s infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes glow{
    from{
        text-shadow:0 0 10px #00ff88;
    }
    to{
        text-shadow:0 0 40px #00ff88;
    }
}

.hero p{
    margin-top:15px;
    font-size:1.2rem;
    max-width:700px;
}

.btn{
    margin-top:30px;
    padding:15px 35px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:50px;
    background:#00ff88;
    color:black;
    font-weight:bold;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:0.4s;
}

.btn:hover{
    transform:scale(1.1);
    box-shadow:0 0 25px #00ff88;
}

section{
    padding:80px 10%;
}

.section-title{
    text-align:center;
    color:#00ff88;
    font-size:2.2rem;
    margin-bottom:40px;
}

.card{
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    padding:25px;
    border-radius:20px;
    margin-bottom:25px;
    transition:0.4s;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(0,255,136,.4);
}

.grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:20px;
}

.footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:30px;
    color:#aaa;
}

.highlight{
    color:#00ff88;
    font-weight:bold;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="bg-animation">
    <span style="left:10%;animation-delay:0s"></span>
    <span style="left:30%;animation-delay:2s"></span>
    <span style="left:50%;animation-delay:4s"></span>
    <span style="left:70%;animation-delay:6s"></span>
    <span style="left:90%;animation-delay:8s"></span>
</div>

<section class="hero">
    <h1>MUHAMMED SHIFAN</h1>
    <p>
        Diploma in Electrical Engineering Student • Football Player • Fitness Enthusiast
    </p>

    <button class="btn" onclick="document.getElementById('about').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
        Explore My Journey
    </button>
</section>

<section id="about">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>

    <div class="card">
        <p>
            I'm <span class="highlight">Muhammed Shifan</span>, 19 years old and currently studying
            <span class="highlight">Diploma in Electrical Engineering (2nd Year)</span>.
            I am hardworking, disciplined, goal-oriented and passionate about football, fitness and personal growth.
            My dream is to build a successful career and make my family proud.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Football Journey</h2>

    <div class="grid">

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Kerala Blasters U15</h3>
            <p>Represented the youth setup and competed at a high level.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Malappuram Team</h3>
            <p>Achieved 3rd place in a Kerala zonal football competition.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Teams Played For</h3>
            <p>FA Soccer Kozhikode, Kerala Blasters, Edumartial, Sporthood and Kerala Team.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>5's Tournament Player</h3>
            <p>Participated in numerous 5-a-side tournaments and became well known in local football circles.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Strengths</h2>

    <div class="grid">

        <div class="card">⚽ Football Intelligence</div>
        <div class="card">💪 Fitness & Gym Training</div>
        <div class="card">🔥 Determination & Discipline</div>
        <div class="card">🤝 Teamwork & Leadership</div>

    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Recognition</h2>

    <div class="card">
        <p>
            Known for exciting performances on the field. Match highlights and football videos showcase
            dedication, technical ability and impact during important games. Recognized by teammates,
            coaches and football fans through consistent performances in youth and local competitions.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="footer">
    © 2026 Muhammed Shifan | Football Portfolio
</div>

</body>
</html>
